Package: footyr
Type: Package
Title: R package to obtain data and statistics about football (soccer) from ISport API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Timothy", "Young", email = "timothyyoung@live.com.sg",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Allows users to easily access data from the ISport API through various 
    functions. Access data on over 1500 leagues/cups worldwide. Get info on team 
    standings, player statistics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Maintainer: Timothy Young <timothyyoung@live.com.sg>
